Notwithstanding the foregoing, **you may copy and modify the Enterprise
Software for development and testing purposes, without requiring a
subscription**. "Development and testing purposes" means non-production
use by an individual or entity for the purpose of evaluating, debugging,
contributing to, or building against the Enterprise Software, and
expressly excludes any use that processes production data, serves end
users (whether internal or external), or otherwise supports a live
business workflow.

You are not granted any other rights beyond what is expressly stated
